data.description: Beautiful Wake Forest home! This large home boasts over 3000 sqft with formal dining room, butler's pantry, spacious kitchen island, and large main floor living area which is perfect for entertaining! Large primary suite with sitting area, private entry to laundry room from primary suite, and guest en suite upstairs! Covered back patio to sit and enjoy your private back yard! Welcome home!
